				\begin{document}$$ {P}_i=\frac{Coverage\  at\ i-th\  position}{Total\  Coverage}=\frac{C_i}{{\displaystyle \sum }{C}_i} $$\end{document}Pi=Coverageati−thpositionTotalCoverage=Ci∑Ciwith P1 + P2 + P3 + … + Pn = 1. The coverage evenness of a transcript can be measured by Shannon’s entropy:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
